  "detailed_description": "Create images/textures based on fractals.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn Fractal Brush you can create images or textures that will surprise you not only when you have created them, but also when creating them!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFractal Brush has more than 100 patterns based on fractals that are the basis of its operation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach pattern is unique, so its behavior when generating fractals is also unique, and it takes a little practice to draw what you want.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt also has the possibility of creating your own patterns and saving them to use them whenever you want.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTips:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1 - Press the \"Esc\" key to access the main menu.<br />\r\n2 - Press the \"Q\" key to quickly access the brush menu.<br />\r\n3 - Press the \"E\" key to quickly access the brush settings.<br />\r\n4 - Press the \"Control\" + \"Z\" keys to undo.<br />\r\n5 - Press the \"Control\" + \"Shift\" + \"Z\" keys to redo.<br />\r\n6 - You can read these and more tips by pressing the \"TUTORIAL\" button.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWARNING: PHOTOSENSITIVE EPILEPSY SEIZURE RISK",
  "about_the_game": "Create images/textures based on fractals.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn Fractal Brush you can create images or textures that will surprise you not only when you have created them, but also when creating them!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFractal Brush has more than 100 patterns based on fractals that are the basis of its operation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEach pattern is unique, so its behavior when generating fractals is also unique, and it takes a little practice to draw what you want.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt also has the possibility of creating your own patterns and saving them to use them whenever you want.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTips:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1 - Press the \"Esc\" key to access the main menu.<br />\r\n2 - Press the \"Q\" key to quickly access the brush menu.<br />\r\n3 - Press the \"E\" key to quickly access the brush settings.<br />\r\n4 - Press the \"Control\" + \"Z\" keys to undo.<br />\r\n5 - Press the \"Control\" + \"Shift\" + \"Z\" keys to redo.<br />\r\n6 - You can read these and more tips by pressing the \"TUTORIAL\" button.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWARNING: PHOTOSENSITIVE EPILEPSY SEIZURE RISK",
